<p class="nx-mt-6 nx-leading-7 first:nx-mt-0"><strong>ArrowHelper(dir :&nbsp;<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="nx-text-primary-600 nx-underline nx-decoration-from-font [text-underline-position:from-font]">Vector3<span class="nx-sr-only nx-select-none"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a>, origin :&nbsp;<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="nx-text-primary-600 nx-underline nx-decoration-from-font [text-underline-position:from-font]">Vector3<span class="nx-sr-only nx-select-none"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a>, length :&nbsp;Number, hex :&nbsp;Number, headLength :&nbsp;Number, headWidth :&nbsp;Number&nbsp;)</strong></p>
<ul class="nx-mt-6 nx-list-disc first:nx-mt-0 ltr:nx-ml-6 rtl:nx-mr-6">
<li class="nx-my-2">dir: 基于箭头原点的方向. 必须为单位向量.</li>
