<li class="nx-my-2">hex: 定义的 16 进制颜色值. 默认为 0xffff00.</li>
<li class="nx-my-2">headLengt: <strong>箭头头部的长度</strong>，默认值为 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">0.2 * length</code></li>
