<p class="nx-mt-6 nx-leading-7 first:nx-mt-0"><code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">AxesHelper</code> 用于在 3D 场景中可视化坐标轴，帮助开发者更直观地理解物体的方向和旋转状态。通常用于调试 <code class="nx-border-black nx-border-opacity-[0.04] nx-bg-opacity-[0.03] nx-bg-black nx-break-words nx-rounded-md nx-border nx-py-0.5 nx-px-[.25em] nx-text-[.9em] dark:nx-border-white/10 dark:nx-bg-white/10" dir="ltr">Three.js</code> 场景中的坐标系。</p>
